data.description: Explore this delightful bungalow tucked away in Washington Heights-an ideal haven for commuters, conveniently located near CTA bus lines and the Dan Ryan/I57 expressway. Enjoy the tranquility of a recently renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, updated flooring on the first floor, and a washer and dryer. This ranch-style home features three bedrooms on the main floor and two additional rooms in the finished basement, currently utilized as bedrooms. Just blocks away from an elementary school and parks, this property boasts a spacious backyard perfect for hosting summertime gatherings. Whether you're looking to expand your investment portfolio or create a personalized home, this is an excellent opportunity.
